## 3. Key Performance Indicators (KPIs)

| Metric | Goal | Tracking Method |
| :--- | :---: | :--- |
| Velocity | < 10 days | Cycle time from 'Backlog' to 'Done' |
| Trust Score | > 95% | Human-in-the-loop (HITL) accuracy check in 'Review' |
| Cost Efficiency | -15% MoM | GPU/API credit burn per story point |

