## 4. Risk/Reward Profile: GenAI Pivot

- **Critical Risk**: Non-Deterministic Technical Debt. Rapidly deploying GenAI features without the "AI Risk Assessment" can lead to a "PoC Graveyard" where models fail in production due to edge-case hallucinations.
- **Strategic Reward**: Hyper-Scalability. Successfully moving "Golden Use Cases" to production creates a reusable "Agentic Framework" that reduces the cost of every subsequent AI project by ~30%.